nhc_headline: ...GABRIELLE ON TRACK TO BRING HURRICANE CONDITIONS TO THE AZORES TONIGHT OR EARLY FRIDAY...
summary: ...GABRIELLE ON TRACK TO BRING HURRICANE CONDITIONS TO THE AZORES TONIGHT OR EARLY FRIDAY... As of 3:00 AM GMT Thu Sep 25 the center of Gabrielle was located near 36.0, -42.3 with movement E at 31 mph. The minimum central pressure was 978 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 85 mph.
